#. TRANSLATORS: Button label for adding a new tag in a list of tags.
msgid "Add tag..."
msgstr "태그 추가..."

msgid "An error occurred. Please try again later."
msgstr "오류가 발생했습니다. 나중에 다시 시도해 주세요."

#. TRANSLATORS: Status message indicating an authorization token for the contact form was created.
msgid "Authorization token created."
msgstr "인증 토큰이 생성되었습니다."

