#. TRANSLATORS: This is the button choice for the question "Really remove this file?" [Cancel] [Remove]
msgctxt "dialog button"
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "취소"

#. TRANSLATORS: SOURCE: <module://zolinga-commons/install/dist/web-components/file-uploader/file-uploader.html> (zolinga-commons:., /html/body/main/div[2]/span)
#. TRANSLATORS: This is the main web form container for the file uploader component
#. TRANSLATORS: This is the instruction for the file uploader component, it should encourage users to click to open file picker dialog or drag and drop files to upload.
msgctxt "File Uploader Component"
msgid "Click or drag and drop files here"
msgstr "파일을 클릭하거나 여기에 드래그하여 업로드하세요."

#. TRANSLATORS: SOURCE: <module://zolinga-commons/install/dist/web-components/file-uploader/file-uploader.html> (zolinga-commons:., /html/body/main/div[1]/span)
#. TRANSLATORS: This is the main web form container for the file uploader component
#. TRANSLATORS: This is the instruction for the file uploader component
msgctxt "File Uploader Component"
msgid "Drop files here to upload"
msgstr "파일을 여기에 드롭하여 업로드하세요"

#. TRANSLATORS: Error shown to the user when sending the contact form email failed.
msgid "Failed to send email, please try again later."
msgstr "이메일 전송에 실패했습니다. 나중에 다시 시도해 주세요."

#. TRANSLATORS: Error shown when the uploaded file has zero size.
msgid "File is empty"
msgstr "파일이 비어 있습니다"

#. TRANSLATORS: Generic file upload error prefix; the specific error is appended.
#, php-format
msgid "File upload error: %s"
msgstr "파일 업로드 오류: %s"

#. TRANSLATORS: Upload status - success message when file uploaded.
msgid "File uploaded"
msgstr "파일 업로드 완료"

#. TRANSLATORS: Upload error when no file was provided in the upload request.
msgid "No file was uploaded"
msgstr "파일이 업로드되지 않았습니다"

#. TRANSLATORS: SOURCE: <module://zolinga-commons/install/dist/web-components/file-uploader/file-uploader.html> (zolinga-commons:., /html/body/main/div[3]/div[1])
#. TRANSLATORS: This is the main web form container for the file uploader component
msgctxt "file removal confirmation"
msgid "Really remove this file?"
msgstr "정말 이 파일을 삭제하시겠습니까?"

#. TRANSLATORS: The text has the following HTML attributes: role="remove-file".
#. TRANSLATORS: This string is inside a <button> element, which is a button / should be concise and as short as possible, follow rules for button text in {{TARGET_LANG}} language.
#. TRANSLATORS: SOURCE: <module://zolinga-commons/install/dist/web-components/file-uploader/file-uploader.html> (zolinga-commons:., /html/body/main/div[3]/div[2]/button[2])
#. TRANSLATORS: This is the main web form container for the file uploader component
#. TRANSLATORS: This is the button choice for the question "Really remove this file?" [Cancel] [Remove]
msgctxt "dialog button"
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "삭제"

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the confirmation button label when user tries to remove a tag, it should be short and clear.
msgid "Remove?"
msgstr "제거하시겠습니까?"

#. TRANSLATORS: Upload error when file size exceeds PHP upload_max_filesize limit. %s is replaced with size in MB.
#, php-format
msgid "The uploaded file exceeds the %s MB"
msgstr "업로드된 파일 크기가 %s MB 를 초과합니다."

#. TRANSLATORS: Upload error when the HTML form MAX_FILE_SIZE directive is exceeded.
msgid ""
"The uploaded file exceeds the MAX_FILE_SIZE directive that was specified in "
"the HTML form"
msgstr "업로드된 파일이 HTML 양식에 지정된 MAX_FILE_SIZE 제한을 초과했습니다."

#. TRANSLATORS: Upload error when the file was only partially uploaded.
msgid "The uploaded file was only partially uploaded"
msgstr "파일이 부분적으로만 업로드되었습니다."
